addStatusHeader

protected void addStatusHeader(HttpServletResponse response)
Used by the various methods that write the response to add a custom HJB header to the response that contains status text representing the result of processing the command.

The name of header is the value of HJBServletConstants.HJB_STATUS_HEADER.
